{"tid":1430867,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會根本垃圾，我地已經輸咗","createTime":"2019-08-08T00:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T14:29:45.000Z","uid":284531,"like":21,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"097942fce48b408b3cfe35fc79c19ec2d1db149f","tid":1430867,"uid":284531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:33:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，呃左大家入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />; 但情況真係好嚴峻，一唔小心鬆懈左我地隨時會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。大家係時候<span style=\"color: red;\">停止圍爐取暖打飛機; 要諗新的文宣手法去突破困局！ 單靠民間記者會我地好快就輸！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yS3gEZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yS3gEZ.png&h=3e8d12ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫巴打推: [正視聽] 乜你地真係覺得今日記者會，真係警察輸左咩？唔好咁天真啦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430493</a><br />\n<br />\n今日會係第三日警察記者會，大家覺唔覺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">開始習慣</span></span>每日下午4點嘅犬隻<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">恥笑大會</span></span>? 沒有最on9，只有更on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。警方一開始所謂的澄稱、推連登撚狗Post和所謂的觀星[槍]實驗，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>根本係有心比位人入去恥笑佢哋。</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可能覺得自己都睇透左冇被影響，咁係因為你覺醒左; <span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>實際上好多人都仲只睇TVB真係會信被洗腦，由淺黃轉返左做中立覺得抗爭者暴力 (我朋友老母就係咁)</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。同埋我發現身邊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經開始有好多圍爐打飛機嘅情況發生，再打落去我地就輸撚緊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>琴晚嘅觀星團係好成功幫大家減壓，我絕對支持; 但真係間中玩一日就好，唔可以持久落去，否則只會變<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">雨傘嘉年華2.0。請大家從今日起停止圍爐打飛機!</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>民間記者會</strong></span>我個人係極支持，係一個關鍵的抗衡手法; 但諗下<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>觀眾會係邊個? 訊息係咪真係傳遞到比廣大市民? 答案係不能！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>CCTVB只會播4點鐘的記招。現時的文宣已經到瓶頸位 (例如<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">9/8 和理飛根本就冇人知)</span></span></strong>，我地必須諗<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新的文宣手法去做宣傳</span></strong></span>！小弟有少少睇法:<br />\n<br />\n1. 組團搞連續的<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">18區放映會，另外搵人剪片</span></strong>(加字幕旁白配音); 內容盡量focus係民間記者會，黑警罪證及我地的訴求！連儂牆要繼續做，但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>已經開始麻木</strong></span>; 所以要播識郁嘅嘢先吸引到人圍觀注意！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEqsJgq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEqsJgq.jpg&h=0a1002a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>全民文宣</strong></span>，人人有責。每日<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>放工放學幫手派傳單、貼街招、幫電視轉台甚至人肉街招</strong></span></span>。我地要吸引到廣大市民的注意。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85KMYR3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85KMYR3.jpg&h=99ad679c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">不定期的勇武抗爭必須繼續</span></strong>，唔可以比狗狗有休息的機會; 否則我地只會被清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fAKtsL9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfAKtsL9.jpg&h=f1ea8c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NmJ2xbp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNmJ2xbp.jpg&h=074afc1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. <strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">9月之前，黎多次全港百萬人大遊行</span></strong>反映民意(此非終極一戰，但有巴打提出過。我知大家未必同意，我只係提出討論。搞的話可以考慮搵民陣吹雞，但行之前一個星期一定要集火瘋狂文宣！係所有人一齊做，不論前線定鍵盤戰士)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h6H6YSX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh6H6YSX.jpg&h=330b6f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後要幫推一下9/8和你飛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DO7R9XV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDO7R9XV.png&h=648d8b01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zmTU7JE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzmTU7JE.jpg&h=b243ab62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kAe9cdE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkAe9cdE.jpg&h=4fb485e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n兄弟爬山，互相幫助<br />\n有禮貌，不分化，不割蓆(核彈都唔割)</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011663fd09ed111bb6787670bf9a239779babe7c","tid":1430867,"uid":50196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:34:23.000Z","msg":"又標題黨.."},{"pid":"aa911b641629aeb493f378a74b327f3f91b4c21e","tid":1430867,"uid":29381,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:34:26.000Z","msg":"玩夠標題未？"},{"pid":"600c88717104934ee08496229345ed7457db4ef3","tid":1430867,"uid":23085,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:34